,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:53:38.000Z","msg":"不過ive嗰d講師應該要返學"},{"pid":"1c9e6bc5e30cec57d6a3cd5e220921850fc4b2d8","tid":1393585,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:57:02.000Z","msg":"支持老師 推"},{"pid":"6a78ff8fa597a593e0c4d5812be8afd1e088790e","tid":1393585,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:57:18.000Z","msg":"1. 徹底撤回逃犯條例 - 政府係有誠意取消就合情合理合法地撤回整個法案<br />\n<br />\n2. 撤回612暴動定性 - 沒有暴徒，只有暴政<br />\n<br />\n3. 必不追究反送中抗爭者 - 沒有特首強推送終條例，何來市民上街示威，更唔會比警察拉<br />\n<br />\n4. 成立獨立委員會，徹查警方濫權濫暴及元朗暴力事件 - 全世界都知香港黑警濫權同警黑合作的問題<br />\n<br />\n5. 全面落實雙真普選 - 最重要一點，一切問題起源，就係特首並非由市民選出，特首不能代表市民意願，不以民為本，只為中央考慮<br />\n<br />\n因此，五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"f4683bff8da538d3fbe84dfb67bc8b2e985e6bd1","tid":1393585,"uid":136393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:57:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b668414c0f4586f0981a4bcb754384e25f4f0ac","tid":1393585,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:57:50.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷<br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"9d60d3cc01e673dcc857ab292458109485432cc7","tid":1393585,"uid":115799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b214ba22dec81d7ca0b3727ef5108057505a9b6c","tid":1393585,"uid":140953,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:58:34.000Z","msg":"講開又講老師同社工都係次次立法會功能組別都係選民主派別，唔明點解仲要無差別咁話人教畜社畜"},{"pid":"582ad395af519dee822e24ebc83e167312b5b027","tid":1393585,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da4bc983d99d3a47a79b6be32c4ff1afa38f5ff","tid":1393585,"uid":212626,"like":0,"disli